com.genband.kandy.api.services.calls

Interface KandyCallServiceNotificationListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    KandyGSMCallServiceNotificationListener

    public interface KandyCallServiceNotificationListener
extends KandyGSMCallServiceNotificationListener
    Interface definition for a callback to be invoked for call operations.

    After receiving the instance of IKandyCallService implementation, this listener must be assigned: 

      Kandy.getServices().getCallService().registerNotificationListener(listener);
    See Also:
    IKandyCallService#registerNotificationListener(KandyCallServiceNotificationListener)}
